<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Zol</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-18 02:20:16</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This is a great great item for the following reasons.<BR>
1) +STR Cloaks are very rare.  The next good +STR cloak that you will find is the Hooded Black Cloak and that sells for well over 10K plat on my server Cazic Thule.<BR>
<BR>
2)  This cloaks is FEATHER LIGHT.  .3 LBS is a great weight savings for anyone so that they can be encumbered less often.  This also makes it the Ultimate non-dragon/plane monk cloak.<BR>
<BR>
3)  This is a rare drop item from the ice goblin king and this guy is well guarded.  He is surrounded by healers and elite goblin guards that melee your casters.  Very tough to crack and I don't think it's soloable.<BR>
<BR>
Add all of thse things together and you have a great cloak, not to mention the DEX for proccing more and the +5 saves to cold never hurts.</font></td></tr></table>
